        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Casualty Loss Deduction Restoration Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill eliminates the suspension period (2018 through 2025) for the tax deduction for personal casualty lossess and increases from $10,000 to $50,000 the limitation on allowable amount of the deduction.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
